collectionMetadata.name: Number & Amount of Claims made under Home Protection Scheme, Annual
collectionMetadata.description:
Number and amount of claims made under Home Protection Scheme in calendar year.

The number of claims refers to approved number of claims for year, on death 
and permanent incapacity grounds under Home Protection Scheme.
Figures prior to 2013 were based on number of claims paid for the year.

The amount of claims refers to sum assured of the approved claims made on death and 
permanent incapacity grounds under Home Protection Scheme. 
Figures prior to 2013 were based on the actual amount paid.
Figures are rounded to the nearest hundred thousand dollars.
